  <h1>API Reference</h1>
  <h2>e!Peek</h2>
  <a href=""><h3>epeek.genome</h3></a>
  <ul>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">startOnOrigin</a>: Starts the plugin either from a gene or any given coordinates</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">start</a>: Starts the plugin using the defined coordinates</li>
    <a href=""><h3>Controls</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">right</a>: Pans the genome browser to the right</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">left</a>: Pans the genome browser to the left</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">zoom</a>: Zooms in/out the genome browser</li>

    <a href=""><h3>Aspect</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">resize</a>: Resizes the genome browser to a new width</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">allow_drag</a>: Sets the response of the genome browser to mouse panning / zooming</li>
    
    <a href=""><h3>Data retrieval</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">get_gene</a>: Gets a gene by name and starts the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">ensGene_lookup</a>: Gets a gene by ensembl ID and starts the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">homologues</a>: Retrieves homology information from the REST API</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">split_homologues</a>: Splits an array of homologues into orthologues and paralogues</li>

    <a href=""><h3>Setters & Getters</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">species</a>: Gets/Sets the species to be used in the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">chr</a>: Gets/Sets the chromosome (or seq_region) to be used in the genome browser/li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">from</a>: Gets/Sets the start coordinate to be used in the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">to</a>: Gets/Sets the end coordinate to be used in the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">gene</a>: Gets/Sets the gene name to be used in the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">genes</a>: Gets the genes currently displayed in the genome browser</li>

    <a href=""><h3>Aspect</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">height</a>: Gets/Sets the height of the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">width</a>: Gets/Sets the width of the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">background_color</a>: Gets/Sets the background color of the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">foreground_color</a>: Gets/Sets the foreground color of the genome browser</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">ease</a>: Gets/Sets the <a href="https://github.com/mbostock/d3/wiki/Transitions#wiki-ease">d3.ease</a> function to use in the genome browser</li>

    <a href=""><h3>Callbacks</h3></a>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">gene_info_callback</a>: Callback called every time a gene is selected</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">ensGenes_callback</a>: Callback called every time an Ensembl gene identifier is searched (normally with the <a href="">get_gene</a> method)</li>
    <li type="circle"><a href="">genes_callback</a>: Callback executed after every pan / zoom event has finished</li>
    
  </ul>
  

